6dd920af3b120babf08d0590ab57","tid":206310,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T14:57:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Good Natured<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無Paraben防腐劑、Phthalate塑化劑、SLS、SLES界面活性劑以及人造色素和香薰等化學成分<br />\n不經動物測試<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://awsassets.wwfhk.panda.org/img/original/collection.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fawsassets.wwfhk.panda.org%2Fimg%2Foriginal%2Fcollection.jpg&h=8aa3a321&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n用左幾支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過護髮素真係會用多左，同用開冇矽嗰啲都有啲唔同"},{"pid":"6485cff95c64f7760e55919653d0cdebe016a0e5","tid":206310,"uid":7488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:00:00.000Z","msg":"Aveda<br />\n好貴 但一次用好少就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894a1f8d517bd5d5903c7bcaa48d7fdfbac3c33b","tid":206310,"uid":22647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:00:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Moist Diane botanical 幾好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經回購2次 洗完好清爽但唔乾</blockquote><br />\n買過粉紅色嗰支<br />\n洗完仲笠過未洗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n綠色冬季用幾唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係用施巴油性髮質洗頭水<br />\n另外orbis有一支mousse狀 非常啱夏天 較適合油頭同幼頭髮嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a0f24989893b9539cb5dfbfd35ea227b2e4245","tid":206310,"uid":82996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:02:30.000Z","msg":"用緊 pureology 好用<br />\nhydrate 個 conditioner 涼涼地好正<br />\n同埋佢寫話可以 massage into scalp"},{"pid":"c52ae5888f24499dba92e63d703fb6a409b1040d","tid":206310,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0