多，我一罌可以 keep 到四五個月都未用完，而且集排毒去角質去頭皮消炎止痕控油清除髮型產品殘留 build up ，洗完頭髮又輕又鬆，陣味又 fresh，deep clean 產品黎講呢隻其實幾全面同非常抵用。<br />\n<br />\nliving proof 隻 full for 我本身較幼髮質洗完頭吹乾後個幾夠 body ，同埋佢既防潮效果真係唔係齋吹水。"},{"pid":"c13390ff7bc01f48da8f16f61f2543abd487d821","tid":206310,"uid":76757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T16:11:36.000Z","msg":"avalon 薰衣草味"},{"pid":"12acb5f17380261177d4779cf4f5fa5103dbc391","tid":206310,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T00:37:27.000Z","msg":"我用緊clear藍色架 我試過咁多隻牌子真係覺得全部都好旱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  得clear好舒服 冇用護髮素個頭都唔旱 應該係啱髮質"},{"pid":"9ae69b6555ac0bacd5bf316cb07195c44a76a9c1","tid":206310,"uid":44267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T01:34:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://g.nordstromimage.com/ImageGallery/store/product/Gigantic/14/_11102874.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fg.nordstromimage.com%2FImageGallery%2Fstore%2Fproduct%2FGigantic%2F14%2F_11102874.jpg&h=5599c2e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻洗完之後d髮質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢隻好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要係椰子味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a014bf3db8b377693a0ac0cbb091a8d5f75cb526","tid":206310,"uid":79281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T02:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac9c06159deb852467207df7ab4be05a7038370","tid":206310,"uid":2022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c